</p><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-cbTzjv cdRhtw pf-43_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-hjGZqJ gtgMXo pf-44_ pf-text-1"><strong>Care Act 2014</strong> - Places a duty on local authorities to safeguard adults at risk of abuse or neglect.



